You could do this faking a click event with jQuery.

Asuming you have two slides, each with 
`$('#slides-1, #slides-2').slides({
  generateNextPrev: true
})`

And your control buttons are `.next` and `.prev`
then you could do

`$('#nextAll').click(function(){
  $('.next').click();
});`

