IMHO what is needed is an auto play in the setup, so once the slideshow is loaded the 'playInterval' clock will start ticking.
. in answer to my own post its easy enough to force an auto play after designated duration.

setTimeout(function(){ 
  $('#slides').slides("play");
}, 1000 );
