amiceli:
An another solution with trigger

HTML : 

```
<div id="slides">
        <a href="#" class="slidesjs-previous slidesjs-navigation" style="display : none">&larr;</a> 
        <a href="#" class="slidesjs-next slidesjs-navigation" style="display : none">&rarr;</a>
</div>
<div class="myNext">Next</div>
```

JS with jquery : 

```
 $('#slides').slidesjs({
        navigation: { 
            active: false,
            effect: "fade" // [string] Can be either "slide" or "fade".
        }
    });
$('.myNext').click(function() {
 $('.slidejs-next').trigger('click');
});
```
